  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<h3>Manager Responsibilities:</h3><ul><li>Delegating responsibilities and supervising business operations</li><li>Hiring, training, motivating and coaching employees as they provide attentive, efficient service to customers, assessing employee performance and providing helpful feedback and training opportunities.</li><li>Resolving conflicts or complaints from customers and employees.</li><li>Monitoring store activity and ensuring it is properly provisioned and staffed.</li><li>Analyzing information and processes and developing more effective or efficient processes and strategies.</li><li>Establishing and achieving business and profit objectives.</li><li>Maintaining a clean, tidy business, ensuring that signage and displays are attractive.</li><li>Generating reports and presenting information to upper-level managers or other parties.</li><li>Ensuring staff members follow company policies and procedures.</li><li>Other duties to ensure the overall health and success of the business.</li></ul><h3>Manager Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in business, management, or related field.</li><li>More education or experience may be preferred or required.</li><li>Strong understanding of business management, financial, and leadership principles.</li><li>Excellent communication, interpersonal, leadership, coaching, and conflict resolution skills.</li><li>Time and project management skills.</li><li>Ability to analyze processes and information, identify problems and trends, and develop effective solutions and strategies.</li><li>Commitment to providing exceptional service to customers and support to staff members.</li></ul>",
